request.description:
Creates a sandbox with unique sandbox id. This call can also be used to create users, accounts etc.
            
            
Sample request:
            
    POST /sandbox
    {
        "sandboxId": "TestSandbox"
    }

Imports sandbox data specified by sandbox id.
            
            
Sample request:
            
    PUT /sandbox/{sandbox_id}
